  • Constructor Details

    • BookingSystem

      public BookingSystem()
      bookableRooms is an ArrayList of the bookable rooms that are created by the user with the interface, it contains:

      • Date and Time Slot of Availability
      • Status of the Room
      • Room code
      • Occupancy of the room
      assistantOnShift is an ArrayList of Assistants that are currently on Shift, it contains:
      • Date and Time Slot of Availability
      • Status of the Assistant
      • Assistants Email Address
      bookings is an ArrayList of Bookings, it contains:
      • A Bookable Room
      • An Assistant on Shift
      • Status of the Booking
      • Student Email
      zipped is a LinkedHashMap that contains pairs of bookable rooms below full occupancy and assistants on shift that are free
